@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> OnHold
OnHold --> Rejected : cancel
Rejected --> Archived : process
Archived --> Created : approve
Archived : entry / log vehicle
Created --> Delivered : review
Delivered --> Processing : reject
Processing --> OnHold : revert
Processing --> [*]
@enduml